                <a style="color:white;margin-left:15%" href="https://www.vakifbank.com.tr/hakkimizda.aspx?pageID=182" target="_blank"> Hakkımızda</a><br /><br /><br />
                <a style="color:white;margin-left:21.2%" href="https://www.vakifbank.com.tr/Default.aspx?pageID=2540" target="_blank"> Kişisel Verilerin Korunması</a><br /><br /><br />
